{"tid":976050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伸「腿」跨障礙　韓有腳車助救災","createTime":"2019-01-10T06:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T06:29:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"802e6acddc18924c5248a2a43e46978d332326ff","tid":976050,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T06:29:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190110/20587785\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190110%2F20587785&d=LthhP1B6BQ%2FTlQrjY2XBYm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=b576f865\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190110%2F20587785&h=5490547b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190110/20587785</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月10日 <br />\n<br />\n伸「腿」跨障礙　韓有腳車助救災<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190110/large/a1503a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190110%2Flarge%2Fa1503a.gif&h=e3bac7e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南韓現代汽車（Hyundai）在拉斯維加斯消費電子展，展示其開發中一款有機械腳的車輛，名為Elevate。車輪裝嵌在四隻機械腳的末端，電動引擎則裝嵌在輪轂中，當它進入崎嶇地段時，就會伸出四腳前進。製造商盼技術能協助救災和服務輪椅使用者，甚至在登陸外星時應用。<br />\n<br />\n現代汽車形容，Elevate可「以哺乳動物或爬行動物的步法移動」，亦可倒後行和左右行駛。公司副主席徐約翰（John Suh，音譯）說：「當海嘯或地震來臨時，救援車隊往往只能運載搜救隊到瓦礫堆邊緣，搜救隊之後就要徒步前進。Elevate則可直達現場，更能越過瓦礫或石屎堆。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190110/large/a1503b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190110%2Flarge%2Fa1503b.gif&h=6d35c006&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n輪椅使用者「自動的士」<br />\n<br />\n有份設計的拜倫指車輛對輪椅使用者而言就像「自動的士」，「它可站起來，走過花槽，直接來到門口，自動調整高低，讓輪椅使用者直接進入車廂」。他補充，車輛可攀越1.5米高的牆和跨越1.5米空隙，車輪更可伸長至相距4.5米的距離，「其間車廂完全平穩」。<br />\n<br />\n英國《泰晤士報》  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n幕僚擅自改圖　澳總理舊鞋變新鞋<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n亞馬遜之父離婚　萬億身家或平分"}]}